    "messages": [
      {
        "turn": 1,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "您好，请问您是贵培训机构/校区的负责人吗？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:42:51.158557",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "喂，你好。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:42:51.158593",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 2,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "您好，请问您是贵培训机构/校区的负责人吗？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:42:58.828323",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 2,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "嗯，我是，你哪位？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:43:07.426658",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 3,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "我是直播平台客服，想跟您聊聊课程发布页的升级。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:43:14.496742",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "哦，什么升级？你说吧，我这边比较忙，简单说。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:43:21.377752",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 4,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "就1分钟，保证简短。我们新增了\"低延迟直播\"选项，发课时可以直接选。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:43:29.284360",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 4,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "嗯，然后呢？跟我现在用的标准直播有什么区别？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:43:35.878223",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 5,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "低延迟直播延迟1-2秒，互动更流畅，适合小班课；标准直播延迟稍长，费用更低。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:43:42.917274",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 5,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "哦，那我现在选的标准直播，需要我自己去改吗？还是你们后台帮我切？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:43:50.886315",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 6,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "之前后台已为您走低延迟线路保障质量，之后发布页会分开显示，您按需选就行。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:44:01.538346",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 6,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "等一下，你说后台已经给我走了低延迟线路？我怎么不知道这事？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:44:09.234950",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "confused"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 7,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "前端当时没开放这个选项，我们临时给您走了低延迟，为保音视频和白板同步。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:44:16.645454",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 7,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "哦……行吧，那现在升级之后我需要做什么操作吗？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:44:24.655756",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 8,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "您是通过Web控制台发课，还是用校务系统或SaaS系统？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:44:32.603275",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 8,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "Web控制台，选的标准直播。你刚不是说已经知道了吗？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:44:39.642395",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "impatient"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 9,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "抱歉确认一下，您的控制台上现在能看到\"低延迟直播\"这个选项吗？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:44:49.160926",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 9,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "我看看啊……等下，我开个网页。嗯，没看到，就只有标准直播和录播两个选项。",
        "tool_calls": [],
