        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 10,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "明白，我这边后台帮您配置一下，明天您再看就有了。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T18:45:09.310554",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 10,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "行，那就等明天看。还有别的事吗？",
